ActPublic Service Employment Act
PrecisAppointment of JANICE CHARETTE, Senior Advisor to the Privy Council Office, of London, England, to act, at pleasure, as Interim Clerk of the Privy Council and Secretary to the Cabinet, effective March 9, 2021, in the stead of Ian Shugart, the Clerk of the Privy Council and Secretary to the Cabinet, until such time as the Clerk resumes his duties.
